## Stack

React + Vite + Tailwind CSS v4 + shadcn/ui (DarkMatter theme)

## Architecture

{{#if hasPopup}}
- `src/popup/` — React popup UI (App.tsx, main.tsx, index.css)
{{/if}}
{{#if hasBackground}}
- `src/background/index.ts` — Service worker (no DOM access, runs in background)
{{/if}}
{{#if hasContentScript}}
- `src/content/index.ts` — Content script (injected into web pages, has DOM access)
{{/if}}
- `src/components/ui/` — shadcn/ui components
- `src/lib/utils.ts` — cn() helper
- `public/manifest.json` — Chrome extension manifest (Manifest V3)
- `public/icons/` — Extension icons (16, 48, 128px)

## Build

Three Vite configs:
- `vite.config.ts` — Popup (React + Tailwind, ES modules)
{{#if hasBackground}}
- `vite.config.background.ts` — Service worker (IIFE, single file)
{{/if}}
{{#if hasContentScript}}
- `vite.config.content.ts` — Content script (IIFE, single file)
{{/if}}

Output: `dist/` with popup.html, assets/, background.js, content.js, manifest.json, icons/

