## Scripts

- `pnpm build` — Build all (popup + background + content)
- `pnpm dev` — Watch mode for all builds
- `pnpm type-check` — Type check without emit
- `pnpm lint` — Lint with Biome
- `pnpm package` — Create ZIP for Chrome Web Store
